// Content slide with bullet points
@slide {
  title: "What is OmniScript?";
  layout: TitleAndContent;
  
  **OmniScript Format (OSF)** is a universal document DSL that unifies:
  
  - Documents (like Markdown)
  - Presentations (like PowerPoint)
  - Spreadsheets (like Excel)
  
  All in a single, plain-text format!
}

// Two-column layout for comparisons
@slide {
  title: "Why OmniScript?";
  layout: TwoColumn;
  
  ## Traditional Approach
  
  - Word for documents
  - PowerPoint for slides
  - Excel for data
  - Binary formats
  - Hard to version control
  
  ## OmniScript Approach
  
  - One format for everything
  - Plain text
  - Git-friendly
  - LLM-friendly
  - Multi-format export
}

